oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Milan Fire Department
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the interior view of Milan Fire Department. There is a two-wheel hand-pulled hose cart behind Fred Dickey and Carl Kastner which held 500 feet of hose. The two men are being honored for 50 years of service.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Uniforms; Men; Fire stations; Chairs
